            <h2><strong><center>INFORMATION</center></strong></h2>
            <hr style="width: 950px;height: 1.5px;background-color: black;"><br>
            <p>
                One of the best tourist places in Tamil Nadu, Ooty, is located in the Nilgiri Hills. The breathtaking view of hills and greenery makes Ooty the “queen of hill stations”. It is a perfect destination for a quick weekend getaway or a romantic holiday.

To explore Ooty, you can opt for a toy train ride. The train runs from Mettupalayam to Ooty. <br>

Ideal Time to Visit: October to May  <br>
Ideal Vacation Duration:  2-3 days  <br>
Average expense: Starting from ₹18,000 (4 days/ 3 nights)  <br>
Places to Visit: Ooty Lake, Rose Garden, Tiger Hill, Botanical Garden and St Stephen’s Church<br>
Things to Do: Photography, exploration, indulging unique cuisines</p>
            
        </div>
